                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8285" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2075</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2247 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">美好生活领创者——保利发展的战略升级之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">A Creator of a Better Life- the Strategic Upgrade Road of Poly’s Development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杨筱恬，关月，朱方伟，李万琦</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">保利发展控股集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略升级；持续竞争优势；战略管理过程；使命；战略制定；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">strategic upgrading, sustained competitive advantage, strategy management process, mission, strategy formulation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例通过保利发展刘董事长在公司30周年庆典现场对公司成长过程的介绍，描述了保利发展从1992年落子广州，到后来的全国规模扩张、业务多元拓展，以及今天的不动产生态平台的战略布局全过程。在此过程中，保利发展通过不断响应内外部环境变化，实现战略升级，进而获取持续竞争优势。通过对本案例的讨论学习，学生将了解战略管理过程的基本要素，明确战略制定的过程是践行使命和实现战略目标的过程，同时也是动态、持续升级的过程，识别公司在战略制定中面临的内外部环境，在此基础上锻炼学生运用理论知识解决实际问题的能力。案例同时也为企业制定战略提供了参考，以帮助企业更好地理解战略管理过程，明确战略制定的逻辑起点应该是企业使命，在制定战略的过程中要时刻对标企业使命与战略目标，确保战略制定和实施的方向不发生偏移，从而制定恰当的战略，并通过战略升级获取持续竞争优势。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Through the introduction of the company&#39;s growth process by Chairman Liu of Poly Development at the company&#39;s 30th anniversary celebration, this case describes an overview of Poly strategic changes from its establishment in Guangzhou in 1992 to its subsequent national scale expansion, diversified business expansion and to today&#39;s real estate ecological platform, which reflects that the strategic management process is composed of multiple aspects such as corporate mission, strategic objectives, strategy formulation and strategy implementation. In the process, Poly has responded to changes in the internal and external environment to achieve strategic upgrades and thereby gain a sustainable competitive advantage. Through the study of this case, students can understand the basic elements of the strategic management process, identify the process of strategy formulation as a process of implementing the mission and achieving strategic objectives, as well as a dynamic and continuous upgrading process, and identify the internal and external environment faced by the company in strategy formulation. Meanwhile the study can increase their ability that apply theoretical knowledge to solve practical problems.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略管理过程；企业使命与战略目标、战略制定；战略升级</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-04</td>
                            </tr>
